---
By: Henry W. Beecher
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 84
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Death
---
Living is death; dying is life. On this side of the grave we are exiles, on
that, citizens; on this side orphans, on that, children; on this side,
captives, on that, freeman; on this side disguised, unknown, on that,
disclosed and proclaimed as the sons of God.
